msgctxt ""
"01160400.xhp\n"
"hd_id3151183\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/swriter/01/01160400.xhp\">AutoAbstract to Presentation</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/swriter/01/01160400.xhp\">ບົດຄັດຫຍໍ້ອັດຕະໂນມັດໄປຫາການນຳສະເໜີ</link>"

#. hNEPz
#: 01160400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01160400.xhp\n"
"par_id3145412\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".uno:SendAbstractToStarImpress\">Opens the current document as a $[officename] Impress presentation. The current document must contain at least one predefined heading paragraph style.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".uno:SendAbstractToStarImpress\">ເປີດເອກະສານປັດຈຸບັນເປັນການນຳສະເໜີ $[officename] Impress. ເອກະສານປັດຈຸບັນຕ້ອງມີຮູບແບບວັກຫົວຂໍ້ທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງອັນ.</ahelp>"

#. RQwem
#: 01160400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01160400.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149801\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Included Outline Levels"
msgstr "ລະດັບໂຄງຮ່າງທີ່ລວມເອົາ"

#. PWVrq
#: 01160400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01160400.xhp\n"
"par_id3153667\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter the number of outline levels to include in the new presentation. For example, if you choose one level, only the paragraphs that follow the \"Heading 1\" paragraph style are included."
msgstr "ປ້ອນຈຳນວນລະດັບໂຄງຮ່າງທີ່ຈະລວມເຂົ້າໃນການນຳສະເໜີໃໝ່. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກໜຶ່ງລະດັບ, ຈະມີສະເພາະວັກທີ່ຖັດຈາກຮູບແບບວັກ \"ຫົວຂໍ້ 1\" ເທົ່ານັ້ນທີ່ຈະຖືກລວມເຂົ້າ."

#. n5oPt
#: 01160400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01160400.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154478\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Paragraphs per Level"
msgstr "ວັກຕໍ່ລະດັບ"

#. ok5os
#: 01160400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"01160400.xhp\n"
"par_id3145580\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter the number of paragraphs that you want to include below each outline level (heading)."
msgstr "ປ້ອນຈຳນວນວັກທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການລວມໄວ້ກ້ອງແຕ່ລະລະດັບໂຄງຮ່າງ (ຫົວຂໍ້)."

#. X5dkE
