#. Aeydu
#: 03050000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"03050000.xhp\n"
"par_id110120150347249577\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Show or hide the vertical ruler. The vertical ruler can be used to adjust page vertical margins, table cells, and object heights on the page."
