#. vpKyU
#: 04020100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04020100.xhp\n"
"par_id3145420\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Type a name for the new section.</ahelp> By default, $[officename] automatically assigns the name \"Section X\" to new sections, where X is a consecutive number."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ພິມຊື່ສຳລັບສ່ວນໃໝ່.</ahelp> ໂດຍເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, $[officename] ຈະກຳນົດຊື່ \"ສ່ວນ X\" ໃຫ້ກັບສ່ວນໃໝ່ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ, ເຊິ່ງ X ແມ່ນຕົວເລກລຽງລຳດັບ."

#. hCR5y
#: 04020100.xhp
