#. iqVaM
#: 04090001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04090001.xhp\n"
"par_id3147167\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Fields are used to insert information about the current document, for example, file name, template, statistics, user data, date, and time.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຟິວຖືກໃຊ້ເພື່ອແຊກຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບເອກະສານປັດຈຸບັນ, ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຊື່ໄຟລ໌, ແມ່ແບບ, ສະຖິຕິ, ຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ໃຊ້, ວັນທີ, ແລະ ເວລາ.</ahelp>"

#. 3tZaF
#: 04090001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04090001.xhp\n"
"par_id911603998090123\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To insert a field in your document, first select the field <emph>Type</emph>, then click in the <emph>Select</emph> list, to choose which information item should be inserted, then click <emph>Insert</emph>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອແຊກຟິວໃນເອກະສານຂອງທ່ານ, ທຳອິດໃຫ້ເລືອກ <emph>ປະເພດ</emph> ຟິວ, ຈາກນັ້ນຄລິກໃນລາຍການ <emph>ເລືອກ</emph> ເພື່ອເລືອກຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຕ້ອງການແຊກ, ແລ້ວຄລິກ <emph>ແຊກ</emph>."

