#. t4SGK
#: 04120221.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04120221.xhp\n"
"par_id3150554\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/tocentriespage/reltostyle\">Positions the tab stop relative to the \"indent from left\" value defined in the paragraph style selected on the <emph>Styles</emph> tab. Otherwise the tab stop is positioned relative to the left text margin.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/tocentriespage/reltostyle\">ວາງຕຳແໜ່ງແທັບທຽບກັບຄ່າ \"ຍໍ້ໜ້າຈາກເບື້ອງຊ້າຍ\" ທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນຮູບແບບຫຍໍ້ໜ້າທີ່ເລືອກໃນແຖບ <emph>ຮູບແບບ</emph>. ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, ຕຳແໜ່ງແທັບຈະຖືກວາງທຽບກັບຂອບຂໍ້ຄວາມເບື້ອງຊ້າຍ.</ahelp>"

