msgctxt ""
"05040600.xhp\n"
"par_id3151168\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Set the height of the footnote area."
msgstr "ຕັ້ງຄ່າຄວາມສູງຂອງບໍລິເວນເຊິງອັດ."

#. RKCwD
