#. TFdj9
#: 05040600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05040600.xhp\n"
"par_id3149807\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/footnoteareapage/maxheight\">Sets a maximum height for the footnote area. Enable this option, then enter the height.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/footnoteareapage/maxheight\">ຕັ້ງຄ່າຄວາມສູງສູງສຸດສຳລັບບໍລິເວນເຊິງອັດ. ເປີດໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກນີ້, ແລ້ວປ້ອນຄວາມສູງເຂົ້າໄປ.</ahelp>"

#. eGwVL
