"05040600.xhp\n"
"par_id3153665\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/footnoteareapage/spacetotext\">Enter the amount of space to leave between the bottom page margin and the first line of text in the footnote area.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/footnoteareapage/spacetotext\">ປ້ອນຈຳນວນໄລຍະຫ່າງທີ່ຈະເຫຼືອໄວ້ລະຫວ່າງຂອບໜ້າລຸ່ມ ແລະ ແຖວທຳອິດຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນບໍລິເວນເຊິງອັດ.</ahelp>"

#. QGmFE
