#. C5KXQ
#: 05040700.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05040700.xhp\n"
"par_id3147170\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"visible\">Specifies where footnotes and endnotes are displayed as well as their numbering formats.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\" visibility=\"visible\">ກຳນົດບ່ອນທີ່ຈະສະແດງເຊິງອັດ ແລະ ໝາຍເຫດທ້າຍເລື່ອງ ລວມທັງຮູບແບບການໃສ່ເລກລຳດັບຂອງພວກມັນ.</ahelp>"

#. SjYBR
#: 05040700.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05040700.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153538\n"
