#. FDdDa
#: 05040700.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05040700.xhp\n"
"par_id3151309\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/footnotesendnotestabpage/ftnntattextend\" visibility=\"visible\">Adds footnotes at the end of the section. If the section spans more than one page, the footnotes are added to the bottom of the page on which the footnote anchors appear.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/footnotesendnotestabpage/ftnntattextend\" visibility=\"visible\">ເພີ່ມເຊິງອັດເຂົ້າຢູ່ທ້າຍເຊັກຊັນ. ຖ້າເຊັກຊັນກວມເອົາຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງໜ້າ, ເຊິງອັດຈະຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າຢູ່ທາງລຸ່ມຂອງໜ້າທີ່ມີຈຸດຍຶດເຊິງອັດປະກົດຂຶ້ນ.</ahelp>"

#. iyfMV
#: 05040700.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05040700.xhp\n"
"hd_id3152960\n"
