"05040800.xhp\n"
"par_id291773262105223\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Defines the character width of the text grid. This option is active when <link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01040900.xhp#square\">Use square page mode for text grid</link> is <emph>not</emph> selected."
msgstr "ກຳນົດຄວາມກວ້າງຂອງຕົວອັກສອນຂອງຕາໜ່າງຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ຈະເຮັດວຽກເມື່ອ <link href=\"text/shared/optionen/01040900.xhp#square\">ໃຊ້ໂໝດໜ້າສີ່ຫຼ່ຽມສຳລັບຕາໜ່າງຂໍ້ຄວາມ</link> <emph>ບໍ່ໄດ້</emph> ຖືກເລືອກ."

