"par_id3153531\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To delete a row, place the cursor in the row that you want to delete, hold down <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline> and press Delete, release, and then press the up or the down arrow."
msgstr "ເພື່ອລຶບແຖວ, ໃຫ້ວາງຕົວຊີ້ໄວ້ໃນແຖວທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການລຶບ, ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">Option</caseinline><defaultinline>Alt</defaultinline></switchinline> ຄ້າງໄວ້ ແລະ ກົດ Delete, ຈາກນັ້ນປ່ອຍແລ້ວກົດລູກສອນຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື ລົງ."

#. Zuiue
