#. ScWpH
#: 05120100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05120100.xhp\n"
"par_id3145822\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/columnwidth/column\">Enter the column number of the column you want to change the width of.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/columnwidth/column\">ປ້ອນລຳດັບເລກຂອງຖັນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປ່ຽນຄວາມກວ້າງ.</ahelp>"

#. DLxMv
