"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/outlinenumberingpage/startat\">Enter the number at which you want to start the heading numbering for the selected level.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/swriter/ui/outlinenumberingpage/startat\">ປ້ອນຕົວເລກທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນການໃສ່ລຳດັບເລກຫົວຂໍ້ສຳລັບລະດັບທີ່ເລືອກ.</ahelp>"

#. VQAuU
#: 06060100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06060100.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149030\n"
