"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>copy field dialog;text documents</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>copying field text;read-only documents</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>read-only documents;copying field text</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ສຳເນົາຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນ ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມໂຕ້ຕອບ;ເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການສຳເນົາຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນ;ເອກະສານອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ເອກະສານອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ;ການສຳເນົາຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນ</bookmark_value>"

#. bRW5A
#: copyfielddialog.xhp
msgctxt ""
"copyfielddialog.xhp\n"
"hd_id781516897374563\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/swriter/01/copyfielddialog.xhp\">Copy Field Content Dialog</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/swriter/01/copyfielddialog.xhp\">ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບຄັດລອກເນື້ອໃນຟິວ</link>"

#. v8tGC
#: copyfielddialog.xhp
msgctxt ""
"copyfielddialog.xhp\n"
"par_id121516897374570\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Copy the content of a field from a read-only document.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຄັດລອກເນື້ອໃນຂອງຟິວຈາກເອກະສານທີ່ອ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງດຽວ.</ahelp>"

#. Uvzza
#: copyfielddialog.xhp
msgctxt ""
"copyfielddialog.xhp\n"
"par_id521516905298162\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In read-only documents the available editing functions are limited. In case of fields, it may be useful to copy part of the field text, but the <link href=\"text/swriter/01/04090005.xhp\">Fields</link> dialog can not be opened."
msgstr "ໃນເອກະສານທີ່ອ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງດຽວ, ຟັງຊັນການແກ້ໄຂທີ່ມີຢູ່ແມ່ນຖືກຈຳກັດ. ໃນກໍລະນີຂອງຟິວ, ມັນອາດຈະເປັນປະໂຫຍດທີ່ຈະຄັດລອກບາງສ່ວນຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນຟິວ, ແຕ່ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <link href=\"text/swriter/01/04090005.xhp\">ຟິວ</link> ບໍ່ສາມາດເປີດໄດ້."

#. umt9q
#: copyfielddialog.xhp
msgctxt ""
"copyfielddialog.xhp\n"
"par_id761516899094991\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <item type=\"menuitem\">Copy Field Content</item>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ຄັດລອກເນື້ອໃນຟິວ</item>."

#. 36k52
#: copyfielddialog.xhp
msgctxt ""
"copyfielddialog.xhp\n"
"par_id521516905298164\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click on the field in the read-only document to highlight it."
msgstr "ຄລິກໃສ່ຟິວໃນເອກະສານທີ່ອ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງດຽວເພື່ອໄຮໄລ້ມັນ."

#. rGvgm
#: copyfielddialog.xhp
msgctxt ""
"copyfielddialog.xhp\n"
"par_id521516905298165\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Right click and select the <item type=\"menuitem\">Copy Field Content</item> item of the context menu."
msgstr "ຄລິກຂວາແລ້ວເລືອກລາຍການ <item type=\"menuitem\">ຄັດລອກເນື້ອໃນຟິວ</item> ຂອງເມນູລັດ."

#. 2bPfh
#: copyfielddialog.xhp
msgctxt ""
"copyfielddialog.xhp\n"
"par_id501516905708560\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can edit and then highlight the desired text in the Content box before pressing the <item type=\"menuitem\">Copy</item> button."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂແລ້ວໄຮໄລ້ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຕ້ອງການໃນກ່ອງເນື້ອໃນ ກ່ອນທີ່ຈະກົດປຸ່ມ <item type=\"menuitem\">ຄັດລອກ</item>."

#. 9vAMn
#: copyfielddialog.xhp
msgctxt ""
"copyfielddialog.xhp\n"
"hd_id341516900303248\n"
