msgctxt ""
"mailmerge04.xhp\n"
"par_idN10543\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/swriter/01/mailmerge04.xhp\">Mail Merge Wizard - Create salutation</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/swriter/01/mailmerge04.xhp\">ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງຈົດໝາຍວຽນ - ສ້າງຄຳຂຶ້ນຕົ້ນ</link>"

#. drFt4
#: mailmerge04.xhp
msgctxt ""
"mailmerge04.xhp\n"
"par_idN10553\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Specify the properties for the salutation.</ahelp> If the mail merge database contains gender information, you can specify different salutations based on the gender of the recipient."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ລະບຸຄຸນສົມບັດສຳລັບຄຳຂຶ້ນຕົ້ນ.</ahelp> ຖ້າຖານຂໍ້ມູນຈົດໝາຍວຽນມີຂໍ້ມູນເພດ, ທ່ານສາມາດລະບຸຄຳຂຶ້ນຕົ້ນທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນຕາມເພດຂອງຜູ້ຮັບໄດ້."

