#. WE5EX
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"par_id521516905298143\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A watermark is an identifying image or pattern in paper that appears as various shades of brightness when viewed by transmitted light. Watermarks were originally created directly during paper manufacturing to discourage counterfeiting of documents, currency bills, stamps and more."
msgstr "ລາຍນ້ຳຄືຮູບພາບ ຫຼື ລວດລາຍທີ່ລະບຸຕົວຕົນໃນເຈ້ຍ ເຊິ່ງຈະປາກົດເປັນລະດັບຄວາມສະຫວ່າງຕ່າງໆເມື່ອເບິ່ງຜ່ານແສງ. ໃນເບື້ອງຕົ້ນລາຍນ້ຳຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃນລະຫວ່າງຂະບວນການຜະລິດເຈ້ຍເພື່ອປ້ອງກັນການປອມແປງເອກະສານ, ທະນະບັດ, ສະແຕັມ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ."

#. XpkJx
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"par_id201516905302881\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use watermarks in %PRODUCTNAME Writer to simulate a paper watermark on the document pages."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ລາຍນ້ຳໃນ %PRODUCTNAME Writer ເພື່ອຈຳລອງລາຍນ້ຳເທິງໜ້າເອກະສານ."

#. EnyKB
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"par_id731516900297974\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Fill the dialog settings below."
msgstr "ຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນການຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນໜ້າຕ່າງດ້ານລຸ່ມ."

#. FhzgC
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"par_id501516905708560\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The values entered applies to the actual page style."
msgstr "ຄ່າທີ່ປ້ອນເຂົ້າຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້ກັບຮູບແບບໜ້າປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. HKvgq
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"hd_id341516900303248\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Text"
msgstr "ຂໍ້ຄວາມ"

#. fkA6z
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"par_id181516900309119\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Enter the watermark text to be displayed as image in the page background.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ປ້ອນຂໍ້ຄວາມລາຍນ້ຳທີ່ຈະສະແດງເປັນຮູບພາບໃນພື້ນຫຼັງຂອງໜ້າ.</ahelp>"

#. Kb3ab
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"hd_id171516900315575\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Font"
msgstr "ຟອນ"

#. A95AE
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"par_id781516900322735\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Select the font from the list.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ເລືອກຟອນຈາກລາຍການ.</ahelp>"

#. mervK
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"par_id1001516900331585\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You cannot choose font size or font style for the watermark text. The text size will be scaled to fit in one line in the page background."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດເລືອກຂະໜາດຟອນ ຫຼື ຮູບແບບຟອນສຳລັບຂໍ້ຄວາມລາຍນ້ຳໄດ້. ຂະໜາດຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະຖືກປັບໃຫ້ພໍດີກັບໜຶ່ງແຖວໃນພື້ນຫຼັງຂອງໜ້າ."

#. WBeAj
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"hd_id721516900337255\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Angle"
msgstr "ມຸມ"

#. rF8xW
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"par_id531516900343270\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Select the rotation angle for the watermark. The text will be rotated by this angle in counterclockwise direction.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ເລືອກມຸມໝູນສຳລັບລາຍນ້ຳ. ຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະຖືກໝູນຕາມມຸມນີ້ໃນທິດທາງທວນເຂັມໂມງ.</ahelp>"

#. SZmr7
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"hd_id511516900348606\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Transparency"
msgstr "ຄວາມໂປ່ງໃສ"

#. xfZe9
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"par_id301516900356824\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Select the transparency level for the watermark. A 0% value produces an opaque watermark and a value of 100% is totally transparent (invisible).</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ເລືອກລະດັບຄວາມໂປ່ງໃສສຳລັບລາຍນ້ຳ. ຄ່າ 0% ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ລາຍນ້ຳທຶບແສງ ແລະ ຄ່າ 100% ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ໂປ່ງໃສທັງໝົດ (ເບິ່ງບໍ່ເຫັນ).</ahelp>"

#. t8xjF
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"hd_id321516900368799\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Color"
msgstr "ສີ"

#. 5TFmS
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"par_id521516900373461\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Select a color from the drop-down box.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ເລືອກສີຈາກກ່ອງລາຍການເລືອກ.</ahelp>"

#. Eabmi
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"hd_id771516906476223\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To change a watermark contents or setting."
msgstr "ວິທີການປ່ຽນເນື້ອໃນ ຫຼື ການຕັ້ງຄ່າລາຍນ້ຳ."

#. YAnUx
#: watermark.xhp
msgctxt ""
"watermark.xhp\n"
"par_id831516906589936\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the watermark in use is a text inserted by the <item type=\"menuitem\">Format - Watermark</item> menu command or by the <link href=\"text/shared/01/classificationbar.xhp\">document classification settings</link>, you can edit the contents and settings on opening the watermark dialog."
msgstr "ຖ້າລາຍນ້ຳທີ່ໃຊ້ຢູ່ແມ່ນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ແຊກໂດຍຄຳສັ່ງເມນູ <item type=\"menuitem\">ຮູບແບບ - ລາຍນ້ຳ</item> ຫຼື ໂດຍ <link href=\"text/shared/01/classificationbar.xhp\">ການຕັ້ງຄ່າການຈັດປະເພດເອກະສານ</link>, ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂເນື້ອໃນ ແລະ ການຕັ້ງຄ່າໄດ້ເມື່ອເປີດໜ້າຕ່າງລາຍນ້ຳ."

